==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Topi
<hw>To"pi</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An antelope
(<spn>Damaliscus corrigum jimela</spn>) having a glossy purplish brown
coat. It is related to the blesbok and is native of East Africa. Also,
any of various related varieties of other districts south of the
Sahara.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Topiarian</ent>⟦br⟧
